0Z","msg":"其實係武力差異極大既形勢下, <br />\n快閃打遊擊係最好選擇,<br />\n集中一區即係比對方部署重兵會師, <br />\n再分配剩餘兵力係會師地點四方八面包抄圍捕<br />\n<br />\n如果只守唔攻, 陣地戰從來都唔係最佳選擇<br />\n就算比你攻到幾個街口, 對方展開左包圍網 你都係要退<br />\n除非你守得住成個區域<br />\n對方通常由幾個唔同方向攻埋黎<br />\n但目前前線顧得前面顧唔到其他, 搞到一有人叫有狗就四散,<br />\n<br />\n咁係因為敵人係四面八方黎, 但大家就打陣地戰, <br />\n只面對一個方向設立單一防線<br />\n簡單D講就係冇形成防守圈, <br />\n以守城做比喻, 固守一門, 其他門開哂<br />\n<br />\n多區開花最低限度係令對方大量分散兵力"},{"pid":"f61d0446975e6975014534baf0eba685887063d3","tid":1612952,"uid":79451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"好多跟本濫捕返黎"},{"pid":"2d1dbd7896dc25706a372b34fd9621c3fa7cd9db","tid":1612952,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"尋日期實好難集中，完全冇車"},{"pid":"814e19b6232afddcd81d9feccc8ac8171fc3ba26","tid":1612952,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"行動派請試下轉為地下組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a12bff5da17c24e7cc4cd0c9fbe7086a599f09","tid":1612952,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"真係太傷"},{"pid":"c4aeac02cccee77df979b2575e642ce2f7c10915","tid":1612952,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"6區示威，1區革命？"},{"pid":"ea489362324ca605d0bfc9fb9bbda15deaa9c929","tid":1612952,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"Agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a216b207632b2ea5ce1709a075be29c2caedfe","tid":1612952,"uid":38461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f61d0446975e6975014534baf0eba685887063d3","tid":1612952,"uid":79451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"好多跟本濫捕返黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"係 其實未必一定同分區有關